metadata.name: COURAGE
metadata.description:
Courage was a courageous woman who demonstrated bravery in the face of adversity.

From the AI Surrealism exhibition at Oculus NYC, hosted by Superchief Gallery NFT and Exquisite Workers. The largest AI art show in history, featuring 100 AI artists, June 2-8, 2023. Curated by Anna Dart and Roger Haus.

KRAN, 2023 [GAN]
